Name: Hang Seng Composite Index
Metadata: Hang Seng Composite Index is a market-capitalization weighted index that comprises the top 200 companies listed on the Main Board of the Stock Exchange of Hong Kong, based on average market cap for the 12 months. The base value of the index is 2000 on base date of January 3rd, 2000.
Data Notes: Currency converted to CAD using Hong Kong Dollars per Canadian Dollar (CADHKD)
